org.sandag.popsyn.domain
Class Target

java.lang.Object
  org.sandag.popsyn.domain.Target
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Target>, org.sandag.common.montecarlo.IWeight
public class Target
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.sandag.common.montecarlo.IWeight, java.lang.Comparable<Target>

Targets are the characteristics of each zone that PopSyn tries to match. Each target involves a single zone and control variable. TargetDao.java and Target.xml map between target records in the database and Target objects.
